{"tid":2449023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣發現野食被加料既經驗","createTime":"2021-03-16T10:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T10:59:45.000Z","uid":82224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8d36d5322398c80d8b467d5db52fe07c851d4c","tid":2449023,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"好多年前我第一次去明將，拎左碟三文魚黎 見到啲色淡到一個點，好奇心驅使下撳開舊三文魚<br />\n<br />\n中間有粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母明將壽司仔，食左兩舊壽司都嘔都嘔唔翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問個侍應佢話紫菜，拿拿聲拎走左 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7834b35f7ed61825f616777e3505eea079f6b2","tid":2449023,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"食五香肉丁麵<br />\n見到肉丁上面有條卷曲嘅毛髮<br />\n重要已經浸到同肉丁一樣色<br />\n應該直接喺罐頭倒出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c2b7a6dec6d52b0942bdc097f08704688b8f48","tid":2449023,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"幾年前喺旺角東間美食快綫買咖哩魚蛋<br />\n畀錢嗰時唔小心跌咗個一蚊銀落兜咖哩汁<br />\n不過嗰個阿姐好淡定<br />\n講咗句「唔緊要」就繼續做下個客生意<br />\n唔知最後邊個食到嗰個一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}